docs.text: q How to ask for VC/investor introduction double opt-out I am happy to help and forward right intros to right people. Please make my help easier with next steps. Do research of investor vc and please specify with investor is a fit in blurb Send me separate forward-able email to each investor so it will be easier for me just forward this email, instead of write many email to each person when you send me just list of investors Example Hi Daniel, I seen that you know {Investor Name}, i think he may be a fit becase he invested in companies in out industry and stage (examples of companies). Can you forward him our blurb? {blurb with 1 paragraph} {bullet points with metrics} ARR EoE growth NRR {link to deck}
